readable.content: A black and white dog leaping through the air as two people watch in the background . A dog 's speed is measured by a man while the dog runs . A small white and black dog is running through a blue netted course while people watch . A wet dog flies through the air while an amazed woman and boy look on . two children watch as a dog runs through a blue fenced course towards a person holding a scanner and microphone .
